                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830430-45-defend612 t17830430-45-punish252"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.)</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. 
               <persName id="t17830430-45-person628">
                  Baron
                   EYRE
